<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" itunes:timing="Word" xml:lang="ja"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="スター(feat. 星乃一歌&amp;天馬咲希&amp;望月穂波&amp;日野森志歩&amp;MEIKO)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Hinomori Shiho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Hoshino Ichika"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Leo/need"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="MEIKO"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Mochizuki Honami"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Tenma Saki"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="アヤメミク"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="メイコ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="天馬咲希"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="天马咲希"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="日野森志步"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="日野森志歩"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="星乃一歌"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="望月穂波"/><amll:meta key="album" value="スター(feat. 星乃一歌&amp;天馬咲希&amp;望月穂波&amp;日野森志歩&amp;MEIKO)"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3318451463"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="50747104"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="xionghiaizi001"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><translations><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en"><text for="L1">【Ichika &amp; Saki &amp; Honami &amp; Shiho】</text><text for="L5">【all】</text><text for="L13">【Ichika】This world that seemed to glittering brightly</text><text for="L14">It was shining dozens of times brighter</text><text for="L15">&quot;I wonder if I can shine in this place?&quot;</text><text for="L16">I say while simply following the sound that ring out with so much love</text><text for="L17">【MEIKO】Within this scenery that changes while everyone is unaware</text><text for="L18">【Saki】I was elated and happy</text><text for="L19">【Honami】then distressed and worried</text><text for="L20">【Shiho】Taking all of that in</text><text for="L21">【Ichika】I put it into a song</text><text for="L22">And I became so strong because of that</text><text for="L23">【MEIKO】&quot;I need you!&quot;</text><text for="L24">I taste such a feeling for the first time</text><text for="L25">【Ichika】The things I was seeing are the things I can see</text><text for="L26">【MEIKO】We&apos;re on our own but we are not alone</text><text for="L27">【Honami】Let&apos;s walk</text><text for="L28">【MEIKO】upon</text><text for="L29">【Shiho】the waves</text><text for="L30">【Saki】while holding our hopes</text><text for="L31">【all】And go, no matter where to!</text><text for="L32">【Ichika】In this SEKAI that continues to be connected to me</text><text for="L33">I was saved, it was like it saved me</text><text for="L34">【Shiho】Though it is tangled up</text><text for="L35">【Saki】Blocked</text><text for="L36">【Honami】And shaken up</text><text for="L37">【MEIKO】it spreads again and again</text><text for="L38">【Ichika】&quot;What we transmit&quot; is so beautiful, don&apos;t you think?</text><text for="L39">Though I still can only see a little ahead in this moment</text><text for="L40">I&apos;ll take in a breath and walk forward, and I&apos;m sure that</text><text for="L41">【Honami】I&apos;ll cry</text><text for="L42">【Saki】Laugh</text><text for="L43">【Shiho】And get angry</text><text for="L44">【MEIKO】But I&apos;ll be satisfied in the end</text><text for="L45">【Ichika】Let&apos;s continue</text><text for="L46">【all】To create</text><text for="L47">【Ichika】The sound of the future in this SEKAI that seems to shine so brightly</text><text for="L48">【MEIKO &amp; Saki &amp; Honami &amp; Shiho】There is not just one color, but multiple gathered together.</text><text for="L49">【Ichika】I didn&apos;t really understand what was going on</text><text for="L50">But I finally realized that I had fun</text><text for="L51">【MEIKO】&quot;All you Need is Love&quot;</text><text for="L52">I shout out such a feeling over and over</text><text for="L53">【Shiho】Until I can love even the disharmonious things</text><text for="L54">【Honami】From being alone to being on our own</text><text for="L55">【Shiho】Me and</text><text for="L56">【Saki】you and</text><text for="L57">【Honami】me and</text><text for="L58">【MEIKO】you, right</text><text for="L59">【Ichika】Now, let&apos;s begin!</text><text for="L60">With this thought that continues to expand</text><text for="L61">I was made, it was like it created me</text><text for="L62">【Shiho】Anytime</text><text for="L63">【Honami】Anywhere</text><text for="L64">【Saki】With anyone</text><text for="L65">【MEIKO】I am connected to them again and again</text><text for="L66">【Saki】I finally managed to voice that &quot;I want you to love me.&quot;</text><text for="L67">【Ichika】Because I take in everything in this moment</text><text for="L68">I&apos;ll accept my feelings too, all the way</text><text for="L69">【Honami】Though I&apos;ll spit it out</text><text for="L70">【Shiho】Go against it</text><text for="L71">【Saki】And grow up</text><text for="L72">【Ichika】I won&apos;t forget the beginning</text><text for="L73">【MEIKO】The sound of the past and me will continue to live</text><text for="L74">【Ichika】I love this SEKAI so much, yet</text><text for="L75">【MEIKO】The flow is getting distorted</text><text for="L76">And correcting it feels like such a difficult thing, but still</text><text for="L77">【Ichika】I love them in the same way as you</text><text for="L78">【MEIKO】This culture</text><text for="L79">【Ichika】This transformation</text><text for="L80">So let&apos;s put them to words without stopping or any embarrassment</text><text for="L81">【Shiho】In this world where I was living alone</text><text for="L82">【MEIKO】All I was doing was watching</text><text for="L83">【Saki】No matter what I tried</text><text for="L84">I didn’t get it and ended up quitting</text><text for="L85">【Honami】I felt afraid in everything that I do</text><text for="L86">【Ichika】If I can show someone the scenery in this moment</text><text for="L87">I wish that it will reach the me in the past</text><text for="L88">【Ichika &amp; Honami】The joy I found when I try</text><text for="L89">【Ichika &amp; Saki】To cry</text><text for="L90">【Ichika &amp; Shiho】To laugh</text><text for="L91">【MEIKO &amp; Ichika】And to get angry</text><text for="L92">【Ichika】I want to continue living with such a feeling!</text><text for="L93">【all】In this SEKAI that continues to shine</text><text for="L94">I was drawn to that song, seems like it was shining</text><text for="L95">【Shiho】That</text><text for="L96">【MEIKO】Heart-throbbing song</text><text for="L97">【Honami】Makes me so happy</text><text for="L98">【Saki】We are connected to each other</text><text for="L99">【Ichika】Each of us was holding an equally shining star</text><text for="L100">【all】Rather than standing out in the darkness</text><text for="L101">I wanna be a star in the center of this world</text><text for="L102">【MEIKO &amp; Honami】So don&apos;t worry</text><text for="L103">【MEIKO &amp; Saki &amp; Shiho】I won&apos;t forget it</text><text for="L104">【Saki &amp; Shiho】In this lifetime</text><text for="L105">【MEIKO &amp; Ichika &amp; Saki】Now, let&apos;s start walking forward.</text><text for="L106">【Ichika &amp; Honami &amp; Shiho】The sound of the future, once again...</text><text for="L107">【MEIKO】The sound of the past, look...</text><text for="L108">【all】Everything shines as &quot;the stars of this planet&quot;.</text><text for="L109">【all】</text><text for="L117">【Ichika &amp; Saki &amp; Honami &amp; Shiho】</text></translation><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans"><text for="L1">【一歌×咲希×穂波×志歩】</text><text for="L5">【全员】</text><text for="L13">【一歌】那看似熠熠生辉的世界</text><text for="L14">实际比想象中的还要绚烂几十倍</text><text for="L15">“我……能在这里发光吗”怀着这样的忐忑</text><text for="L16">我只是循着由无数爱奏响的旋律前行着</text><text for="L17">【MEIKO】不觉间流转的景色中</text><text for="L18">【咲希】时而因为欢欣而雀跃</text><text for="L19">【穂波】时而因为苦闷而辗转</text><text for="L20">【志歩】将万千感受尽数接纳</text><text for="L21">【一歌】融汇成一首歌</text><text for="L22">就这样淬炼出如今的坚强</text><text for="L23">【MEIKO】“我需要你！”</text><text for="L24">这样的心情 还是初次体会到</text><text for="L25">【一歌】从“被看见的风景”变成了“能被别人看见的存在”</text><text for="L26">【MEIKO】虽孑然一身却不觉得孤独</text><text for="L27">【穂波】让我们</text><text for="L28">【MEIKO】踏浪</text><text for="L29">【志歩】前行</text><text for="L30">【咲希】怀抱希望</text><text for="L31">【全员】奔向无尽的远方！</text><text for="L32">【一歌】在这永恒相连的SEKAI里</text><text for="L33">我似乎既被拯救 同时也在拯救他人</text><text for="L34">【志歩】就算彼此纠缠</text><text for="L35">【咲希】被阻塞</text><text for="L36">【穂波】被动摇</text><text for="L37">【MEIKO】仍无数次将心扉敞开</text><text for="L38">【一歌】“心意相通”这样的事 是多么美好啊</text><text for="L39">就算现在还只能看到一点点</text><text for="L40">我也一定会呼吸着 继续前行</text><text for="L41">【穂波】哪怕哭泣</text><text for="L42">【咲希】哪怕欢笑</text><text for="L43">【志歩】哪怕愤怒</text><text for="L44">【MEIKO】最后都会迎来喜悦</text><text for="L45">【一歌】然后继续去编织</text><text for="L46">【全员】属于未来的旋律</text><text for="L47">【一歌】在流光溢彩的SEKAI里</text><text for="L48">【MEIKO×咲希×穂波×志歩】汇聚着斑斓多彩的色泽</text><text for="L49">【一歌】虽然曾不明白这一切究竟是什么</text><text for="L50">但终于意识到 那正是快乐本身</text><text for="L51">【MEIKO】“你所要的是‘爱’呀”</text><text for="L52">这样的心情 我会一次次呐喊</text><text for="L53">【志歩】直到连无法相容的事物都能去爱</text><text for="L54">【穂波】从“孤独的个体”蜕变为“独立的人”</text><text for="L55">【志歩】无论是我</text><text for="L56">【咲希】是你</text><text for="L57">【穂波】是她</text><text for="L58">【MEIKO】都是如此</text><text for="L59">【一歌】来吧 开始吧！</text><text for="L60">随着这不断扩散的情感</text><text for="L61">我似乎既被塑造 亦在主动创造</text><text for="L62">【志歩】无论何时</text><text for="L63">【穂波】无论何地</text><text for="L64">【咲希】无论是谁</text><text for="L65">【MEIKO】我们一次又一次地彼此相连</text><text for="L66">【咲希】终于能开口说出“请爱我吧”</text><text for="L67">【一歌】因为我已经能接受现在所有的一切</text><text for="L68">所以也请接纳我的心意 直到永远</text><text for="L69">【穂波】尽情倾诉</text><text for="L70">【志歩】奋力抗争</text><text for="L71">【咲希】即使变得成熟</text><text for="L72">【一歌】也不会忘记最初的起点</text><text for="L73">【MEIKO】伴随着至今的旋律 我将继续生存下去</text><text for="L74">【一歌】对于这个SEKAI 明明只是怀揣着最纯粹的爱意</text><text for="L75">【MEIKO】却发现它在一点点扭曲 试图纠正偏离的洪流</text><text for="L76">虽知此事艰难</text><text for="L77">【一歌】但我仍然像你一样去爱着</text><text for="L78">【MEIKO】珍视这份文化</text><text for="L79">【一歌】拥抱这份变化 永不停止地</text><text for="L80">毫不羞怯地 将其化作言语</text><text for="L81">【志歩】在曾经孤身生活过的 那个世界里</text><text for="L82">【MEIKO】我仅是冷眼旁观 仅此而已</text><text for="L83">【咲希】无论做什么 无论挑战什么</text><text for="L84">都因迷茫 而半途而废</text><text for="L85">【穂波】做任何事情 都让我心生畏惧</text><text for="L86">【一歌】如果此刻的景色能被传递</text><text for="L87">我愿告慰过去彷徨的自我</text><text for="L88">【一歌×穂波】试着哭泣</text><text for="L89">【一歌×咲希】试着欢笑</text><text for="L90">【一歌×志歩】试着愤怒</text><text for="L91">【MEIKO×一歌】方才察觉到的喜悦</text><text for="L92">【一歌】正是我愿为之生存下去的意义！</text><text for="L93">【全员】在这永恒闪耀的SEKAI里</text><text for="L94">我似乎被吸引着 也在发光着</text><text for="L95">【志歩】“曾有首歌</text><text for="L96">【MEIKO】让我心潮激荡</text><text for="L97">【穂波】那时光如此欢畅”</text><text for="L98">【咲希】“我们，心意相通”</text><text for="L99">【一歌】我们都拥有同样璀璨的星</text><text for="L100">【全员】比起在黑暗中显眼</text><text for="L101">我更愿成为世界中央的一颗星</text><text for="L102">【MEIKO×穂波】没关系</text><text for="L103">【MEIKO×咲希×志歩】我不会忘记的</text><text for="L104">【咲希×志歩】此生不渝</text><text for="L105">【MEIKO×一歌×咲希】来吧，就此启程吧</text><text for="L106">【一歌×穂波×志歩】未来的旋律…</text><text for="L107">【MEIKO】过往的乐章…</text><text for="L108">【全员】看啊 一切都在闪耀 “这颗星球上将绽放光芒”</text><text for="L109">【全员】</text><text for="L117">【一歌×咲希×穂波×志歩】</text></translation></translations><songwriters/><transliterations><transliteration xml:lang="ja-Latn"><text for="L13"><span begin="22.053" end="22.255" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">hi ka</span> <span begin="22.255" end="22.475" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ri</span> <span begin="22.475" end="22.840" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ka ga ya</span> <span begin="22.840" end="22.901" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">i</span> <span begin="22.901" end="23.012" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">te</span> <span begin="23.012" end="23.103" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">mi</span> <span begin="23.103" end="23.324" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">e</span> <span begi